1
00:00:03,145 --> 00:00:06,762
We know that everything 
has to be consistent,

2
00:00:06,762 --> 00:00:12,087
so here, 
where we’re being told how,

3
00:00:12,087 --> 00:00:14,044
how to make our approach.

4
00:00:14,275 --> 00:00:17,516
[Love | The Greatest Invention]

5
00:00:17,624 --> 00:00:21,653
Cakravartī Ṭ􏰅hākur is saying

6
00:00:22,992 --> 00:00:26,489
the method invented
by the braja-gopis …

7
00:00:26,526 --> 00:00:31,091
there’s no superior way 
to worship the Lord.

8
00:00:31,721 --> 00:00:36,385
aradhya bhagavan vrajesa-tanayas
[Śrīla Viśvanātha Cakravartī Ṭ􏰅hākur]

9
00:00:36,541 --> 00:00:39,487
Who’s the lord of Vrindavan, 
in other words?

10
00:00:39,487 --> 00:00:42,079
His tanay, his son.

11
00:00:42,341 --> 00:00:45,563
vrajesa-tanayas tad-dhama vrindavanam

12
00:00:45,948 --> 00:00:51,598
And His land, Vṛndāvan,
what is it characterized?

13
00:00:51,687 --> 00:00:56,927
Mercy over justice, 
heart over intellect,

14
00:01:01,164 --> 00:01:05,701
where love and affection
reign supreme.

15
00:01:06,249 --> 00:01:12,978
So he can only be captured 
by love and affection.

16
00:01:13,736 --> 00:01:17,529
He’s not impressed 
with any display of intellect,

17
00:01:17,529 --> 00:01:26,745
mental prowess, miracles, 
yogic sidhis,

18
00:01:26,745 --> 00:01:28,591
any such thing.

19
00:01:30,121 --> 00:01:34,914
But heart. The power
of love and affection.

20
00:01:35,037 --> 00:01:36,220
Sometimes
Guru Mahārāj says

21
00:01:36,220 --> 00:01:39,910
it’s the greatest thing 
ever invented.

22
00:01:40,567 --> 00:01:42,028
Aspired to.

23
00:01:43,242 --> 00:01:49,717
What is admittedly driving 
everyone in this world,

24
00:01:51,083 --> 00:01:55,995
searching for love, 
sweetness, affection,

25
00:01:57,197 --> 00:02:02,052
it’s the goal, 
the target of everyone.

